Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:50.08,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}我們的心明明曾相連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:58.00,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}動搖的眼眸卻保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.06,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}不論多麼堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:04.66,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}不論多想傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:10.77,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}我的聲音你都聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:15.63,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}光之冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:20.51,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}都銘刻於此身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:25.65,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}在此舉步前行
