Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:33.30,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}動搖的視線卻不再相接
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:36.43,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}不論失去幾分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:39.89,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\fad(300,300)}不論幾度錯過
